title: Improved Shock Absorbers and Spring Coils On Loyales
url: Improved Shock Absorbers and Spring Coils On Loyales
author: Loyale 2.7 Turbo
content: Most of these cars still have their original shock absorbers and springs. Loyale 2.7 Turbo has done the hard work of hunting down springs and struts that are often cheaper and easier to find than OEM Subaru replacements.
